title: Mehmood Ahmed wins PP-55 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Mehmood Ahmed of Tehreek-e-Labbaik Pakistan has won the election from Punjab Assembly constituency PP-55 Narowal-II by securing 33,793 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Arslan Hafeez an independent candidate who bagged 24,091 votes.
Votersâ€™ turnout remained 49.22 percent.
